                    />

        <div class="bb-intro-module__card-description">
                    <p>Texas lawmakers <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/texas-abortion-ban-exceptions-deaths">pushed for new exceptions to the state’s strict abortion ban</a> after we reported on the deaths of pregnant women whose miscarriages went untreated.</p>

            </div>
</div>

        
<div class="bb-intro-module__card ">
            
    


    <img
        class="bb-intro-module__art"
        alt=""
        width="400"
        height="400"
        loading="lazy" js-autosizes        src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/2023113-Ethics-Code.jpg?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=800&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=bef937d6f2c382c24d2579a21fbe4faa"
