            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/missouri-abortion-amendment-republican-bill-proposals">
                                    Missouri Voters Enshrined Abortion Rights. GOP Lawmakers Are Already Working to Roll Them Back.
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
